        "JAVANGLE_MYST_BODY_BASEFORM_BLOCK_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Tene</style> ut damnum frontale veniens drastice minuas, <style=cIsUtility>Limitem</style> secundum damnum blocatum obtinens. Si <style=cIsUtility>recte temporatum</style>: damnum ab omnibus directionibus nullificat, artem refrigerat, <style=cIsUtility>Potentiam Magicam</style> secundum damnum blocatum restituit, <style=cIsUtility>Limitem duplicem</style> obtinet et usque ad <style=cIsDamage>3x damnum</style> blocatum hostibus propinquis reflectit.",
